What's for dinner?

45
00:04:18,980 --> 00:04:20,440
Sesame Tofu.

46
00:04:22,050 --> 00:04:24,510
You may complain
Tofu is all I feed you.

47
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:27,250
But sesame Tofu isn't
made from soy.

48
