from the very beginning.

88
00:09:33,620 --> 00:09:35,650
No, this is the first time.

89
00:09:37,390 --> 00:09:40,230
You've cherished me for
a hundred years.

90
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:46,660
Can you now wait another
undred for me?

91
00:09:49,710 --> 00:09:51,970
As you know, the sun rises.

92
00:09:52,680 --> 00:09:56,840
And then it sets.

93
00:10:00,420 --> 00:10:05,290
The big red sun travels
from east to west.

94
00:10:06,690 --> 00:10:10,220
Every single day
it completes its journey.

95
00:10:12,230 --> 00:10:17,100
So can you not wait for me?

96
00:10:20,300 --> 00:10:22,100
It matters not to me...

97
00:10:23,540 --> 00:10:30,170
...that you may find another
to love when I am gone.

98
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:35,280
And with that...

99
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:38,680
...my time to die has come.

100
00:10:45,160 --> 00:10:47,760
Bury me with the goldfish.

