When I was a girl...

176
00:26:25,370 --> 00:26:30,460
...many stone statues lined
the mountain path near my house.

177
00:26:31,310 --> 00:26:33,900
I used to play there.

178
00:26:35,080 --> 00:26:36,440
One day...

179
