01:39:49,370 --> 01:39:52,960
Next, itis heated to 80 degrees
in a large pot.

538
01:39:53,140 --> 01:39:57,130
And special, succulent slices
are added for flavor.

539
01:39:58,710 --> 01:40:01,180
Itis then simmered to perfection.

540
01:40:01,810 --> 01:40:04,650
Next, is our most
secret ingredient.

541
01:40:12,920 --> 01:40:15,950
Special, selected spices
make for a perfect finish.

542
01:40:32,580 --> 01:40:37,040
What a waste.
That was made especially for you.

543
01:40:37,250 --> 01:40:38,370
You can't be serious!

544
01:40:38,520 --> 01:40:40,350
That's not pig,
it's human!

545
01:40:40,520 --> 01:40:41,510
Culinary Armageddon!

546
01:40:41,650 --> 01:40:44,850
A filthy, self-absorbed killer,
like you,

547
01:40:44,990 --> 01:40:47,720
deserves nothing less than that!

548
01:40:48,160 --> 01:40:49,280
Who the hell are you?

549
01:40:53,660 --> 01:40:57,000
At that moment,
he recalled the words of his friend,

550
01:40:57,130 --> 01:40:59,690
Gennai Hiraga, the inventor.

551
01:40:59,840 --> 01:41:03,330
If you're ever in the clutches of
maddened monsters,

552
01:41:03,470 --> 01:41:05,470
just push this button.

553
01:41:06,040 --> 01:41:09,100
No need.
It's highly unlikely to happen.

554
01:41:09,580 --> 01:41:10,670
Now!

555
01:41:15,950 --> 01:41:17,420
Thank you, Gennai.

556
01:41:31,640 --> 01:41:32,500
Fart attack!

557
01:41:44,850 --> 01:41:48,280
Shall I show you my true self?

558
01:42:17,380 --> 01:42:18,440
You stink!

559
01:42:18,720 --> 01:42:19,910
Smells like shit.

560
01:43:30,920 --> 01:43:32,010
Forgive me.

561
01:43:32,520 --> 01:43:35,010
I'l never kill anyone again.

562
01:43:35,160 --> 01:43:37,790
I'am so sorry.
Please forgive me.

563
01:43:37,930 --> 01:43:39,160
I'm sorry.

564
01:43:39,360 --> 01:43:41,760
I beg you.
Please.

565
01:43:42,570 --> 01:43:44,230
I'm really very sorry.

566
01:43:44,600 --> 01:43:45,730
I apologize.

567
01:43:45,840 --> 01:43:48,570
I'm ever so sorry.
Forgive me.

568
01:43:58,320 --> 01:44:00,580
Is that right?

569
01:44:04,190 --> 01:44:05,950
How did you get hurt?

570
01:44:06,260 --> 01:44:08,520
You never mentioned that.

571
01:44:10,090 --> 01:44:11,190
This, you mean?

572
01:44:11,360 --> 01:44:13,460
As I was on my way back...

573
01:44:21,140 --> 01:44:23,540
-That's all.
-Really?

574
01:44:25,210 --> 01:44:27,040
I'd better get some sleep.

575
01:44:27,210 --> 01:44:29,980
It's time to die.

576
01:44:35,990 --> 01:44:42,150
But Shotaro did not die.
He lived on until his 138th year.

577
01:44:42,330 --> 01:44:46,460
And he became the world's
first astronaut.

578
01:44:46,860 --> 01:44:50,820
No way!
That'll never happen to me.

579
01:44:51,270 --> 01:44:52,260
It happened!

580
01:44:53,100 --> 01:44:54,230
Thank you, Gennai.

581
01:44:54,500 --> 01:45:00,470
The End

582
01:45:10,820 --> 01:45:12,760
A hundred years...

583
01:45:16,760 --> 01:45:18,920
Is it here already?

584
01:45:19,530 --> 01:45:22,860
"Ten Nights of Dreams"

585
01:45:23,770 --> 01:45:26,260
Or will it take another
hundred years?

